 
<p>
The "law and order"
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2023/may/10/police-britain-private-security-firms-powers">Tories have made big cuts in cops</a>
on the street. So landlords pay to replace them, in some local areas, with private
security guards who enforce unpublished secret rules, and get away
with violence just like official <a class=glossary href="/glossary.html#thug">thugs</a>.

